title: Lucinda Williams (Live on KEXP at Home)
description: Veteran Nashville-based singer-songwriter Lucinda Williams shares an exclusive set of songs from her recent, and 15th, album, Good Souls Better Angels, and talks to Cheryl Waters live on KEXP on Thursday, August 13, at 3pm PT.
